{"tid":1901071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒系列7: 消息：蘋果日報裁員至少21人 不涉編採部門","createTime":"2020-02-27T15:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T14:09:28.000Z","uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"196d84afe05fdc305974a4fcf77454ed4aff16ee","tid":1901071,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】消息指，蘋果日報裁員至少21人，主要涉及營業和市場部。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，因疫情影響廣告業務，蘋果日報印刷及數碼業務合併，會裁減員工。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒工會發言人林偉聰表示，星期三接獲同事求助，據悉至少涉及21名員工，主要是營業和市場部，並不涉及編採部門，他指工會會與管理層會面，跟進及了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9121%E4%BA%BA-%E4%B8%8D%E6%B6%89%E7%B7%A8%E6%8E%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80-122635916.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%259121%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E6%258E%25A1%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2596%2580-122635916.html&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0eoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=bc36fc7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9121%E4%BA%BA-%E4%B8%8D%E6%B6%89%E7%B7%A8%E6%8E%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80-122635916.html</a>"},{"pid":"744cdb99e4873e4f2d0f0da10c7d90a0f46b2026","tid":1901071,"uid":65598,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"死左膠無尾BEAR (#292292) 死五毛屈手足<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601170/page/38\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601170/page/38</a><br />\n留言881開始屈手足亂打人, 但又無證據<br />\n<br />\n&quot;依家係無証據話廢老先打人， 但有証據前線打人呀， 你有片既請share出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我同你say sorry&quot;"},{"p